This file describes 'standard' McStas parameter names for components of different
classes.

Dimensions:
radius
xwidth
yheight
zdepth
thickness
w1 h1 w2 h2 l
R0 Qc alpha m W
length
nslit

Physical parameters:
sigma_abs
sigma_inc
sigma_coh
nu
phase

Monte Carlo parameters:
p_interact
focus_xw
focus_yh
focus_aw
focus_ah

Other:
filename
